name: Saving Your Life
description:
Hello! Welcome to my shop!

Any size print is available for EVERY photo, regardless of the size in the actual listing. If a shot is only available in a specific size, I'll be sure to specify. Prices and sizes are as follows:

4x6 - $10
5x7 - $15
8x10 - $20

All prints are sent unframed and unmatted, with a signature on the back. The photo will NOT be watermarked. If you should have a special request, questions, or just wanna give some feedback, please contact me through a big cartel message, or @ cilrinsight [!at] gmail.com!

Thanks for stoppin' by!
